data.description: Tastefully updated 3 bedroom & 3 bath home on a half acre lot! Updated features throughout! You are greeted with a beautiful earth tone accent wall as you enter the living room which opens to the pristine kitchen and dining area. White shaker cabinets, subway tile and stainless steel appliances including a gas stove range. TWO huge en-suite bedrooms! The master bedroom has it's own entry to the backyard. Massive covered RV parking that leads right to an entertainer's dream backyard! Design to your liking and create your own paradise! The possibilities are endless with this large lot! It also features two barns in the back, three car garage and all new windows! It's all powered by solar! Make it your own today!
